<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Key C (no sharps/flats). Strong C-F-G-Am progression throughout.
- LH: C: C2-G2-C3-E3; F: F2-C3-F3-A3; G: G2-D3-G3-B3; Am: A2-E3-A3-C4.
- Climax bar 5-6: Full high register C5-D5-E5, RH A5-F5.
- B° passing chord bar 5 acknowledged in RH with B4-D5 thirds.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
- Ascending melody bar 5 E5 sustained in RH G5-G5.
- Bass stepwise: C-F-G-Am-C-Dm-G-F-Am-Dm-C (clear tonal motion).
- F#/G# in bar 4 (secondary dominant), LH stays diatonic G2-D3-G3-B3.

TEXTURE ARC:
- Pickup + bars 1-2: moderate, establishing C tonic
- Bars 3-4: rising chromatic tension
- Bars 5-6: climax, high register RH
- Bars 7-8: return and resolution to C
-->
